---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { siteMetadata } from '../data/data';
---

<Layout title="About | Asu Pınar Aksu" description="Learn more about Asu Pınar Aksu — a research-driven Product Designer specializing in user research, data analysis, and user-centered digital products.">
    <section class="py-12 md:py-20 max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">About</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 leading-[1.1] mb-12">
            Research-driven design<br />for meaningful products.
        </h1>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
                I'm <strong class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Asu Pınar Aksu</strong> — a Product Designer with a research-driven approach, specializing in user research, data analysis, and insight generation to create user-centered, meaningful experiences and impactful digital products.
            </p>
            <p>
                With experience spanning B2B and B2C platforms at companies like <strong class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Migros One</strong> and <strong class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">ebebek</strong>, I've led end-to-end design processes — from field observations and customer journey mapping to interactive prototyping and stakeholder alignment.
            </p>
            <p>
                Beyond design, I've served as a <strong class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Scrum Master</strong>, optimizing team workflows and championing a user-centered culture across cross-functional teams including product, CRM, and data.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Experience -->
        <div class="mt-24 pt-16 border-t border-neutral-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-12">Experience</h2>
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div class="group">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight">Expert Product Designer</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-1 md:mt-0">Mar 2025 – Sep 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Migros One · İstanbul</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Conducted field observations for B2B and B2C systems used by store staff and couriers, collaborated with product managers to evaluate operational issues, and designed user-centered interfaces.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="group">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight">Product Designer</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-1 md:mt-0">Dec 2023 – Mar 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">ebebek · İstanbul</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Designed user-centered interfaces for B2C web, mobile web, and app platforms. Mapped customer journeys, collaborated with CRM and data teams, and served as Scrum Master for the Post-Order team.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="group">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight">Jr. UX/UI Designer</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-1 md:mt-0">Jul 2023 – Dec 2023</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">ebebek · İstanbul</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Created comprehensive user journey maps and designed user-centered interfaces leveraging insights from user research.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="group">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight">UX/UI Designer</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-1 md:mt-0">Apr 2023 – Jun 2023</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Askipo · İstanbul</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Designed user-centered interfaces and developed design systems and guidelines to ensure consistency and usability standards.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="group">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between mb-2">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight">Jr. UI/UX Designer</h3>
                        <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-1 md:mt-0">Jan 2023 – Mar 2023</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Neon Apps · İstanbul</p>
                    <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Supported UI kit creation and development of design system foundations in Figma.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Education -->
        <div class="mt-24 pt-16 border-t border-neutral-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-12">Education</h2>
            <div>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between mb-2">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight">Yıldız Technical University</h3>
                    <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-1 md:mt-0">2019 – 2023</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">Bachelor's Degree · Computer Education and Instructional Technologies</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Skills & Tools -->
        <div class="mt-24 pt-16 border-t border-neutral-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-12">Skills & Tools</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Design</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Figma, Illustrator</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Research</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Usability Testing, User Interviews, Field Research, UX Strategy</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Slack, Trello, Miro, Airtable, Jira</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Leadership</h3>
                    <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Scrum Master</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-24 pt-16 border-t border-neutral-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-4">Want to work together?</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-500 mb-8">I'm currently open to new projects and collaborations.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex px-8 py-4 bg-neutral-900 text-white font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-all duration-300">
                Get in Touch
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
